        <div><p>The fields of wild flowers, dried and shriveled</p>

<p>tamed by power. Mowed down for convenience. </p>

<p>No one would walk this hills to see wild flowers</p>

<p>Now plucked, gone.</p>

<p>Genetically engineered and packaged and patented</p>

<p>Take this seed and we will plant it.</p>

<p>We know best</p>

<p>We provide the water, light.</p>

<p>Grow your seed. Blossom your network</p>

