      <div class="annotationBody">
        
        <div><p>Every morning
I save a firefly
that has wandered
into the house
lured by an LED 
I suppose.
I do it 
selfishly.
My grandchildren
will appreciate
future generations
I have afforded
by gently 
saving their ancestors.</p></div>
