<p>However, in Germany there is a lot of censorship and lots of media pages disable comments because they don't want to hear the opinion of the readers (which often question the messages of their articles). </p>

<p>I think there have to be real legal reasons for disabling comments -- not just "you can't debunk my lies".</p>

